# Lynis Fleet — Configuration des serveurs
# Format : NOM|USER@IP|CLE_SSH
# Laissez CLE_SSH vide pour la machine locale (audit local sans SSH)
#
# Exemples :
#   LOCAL||                                    → audit local (pas de SSH)
#   WEB1|deploy@10.0.0.2|~/.ssh/id_deploy     → serveur distant via SSH
#   WEB2|deploy@10.0.0.3|~/.ssh/id_deploy     → meme cle SSH, autre serveur
#   DB1|admin@10.0.0.10|~/.ssh/id_db          → cle differente

LOCAL||
# WEB1|deploy@10.0.0.2|~/.ssh/id_deploy
# WEB2|deploy@10.0.0.3|~/.ssh/id_deploy
# DB1|admin@10.0.0.10|~/.ssh/id_db
